# Wire Harness Cost Management System - Backend

와이어 하네스 매입 단가 관리 시스템 백엔드 API

## Quick Start

### Prerequisites

- Python 3.11+
- pip

### Installation

```bash
# Create virtual environment
python -m venv venv

# Activate virtual environment
source venv/bin/activate  # Linux/macOS
# or
.\venv\Scripts\activate  # Windows

# Install package with dev dependencies
pip install -e ".[dev]"
```

### Run Development Server

```bash
uvicorn backend.main:app --reload
```

API documentation: http://localhost:8000/docs

### Run Tests

```bash
# Run all tests
pytest

# Run with coverage
pytest --cov=backend --cov-report=html

# Run specific test file
pytest tests/test_setup.py -v
```

### Code Quality

```bash
# Linting
ruff check .

# Formatting
ruff format .

# Type checking
mypy backend/
```

## Project Structure

```
backend/
├── backend/                # Main package
│   ├── config/             # Configuration
│   ├── domain/             # Core business logic
│   │   ├── entities/       # Business entities
│   │   ├── repositories/   # Repository interfaces
│   │   ├── services/       # Domain services
│   │   └── value_objects/  # Value objects
│   ├── application/        # Use cases layer
│   │   ├── use_cases/      # Business use cases
│   │   ├── dtos/           # Data transfer objects
│   │   └── interfaces/     # External interfaces
│   ├── infrastructure/     # External implementations
│   │   ├── persistence/    # Database (SQLAlchemy)
│   │   ├── excel/          # Excel processing
│   │   └── pdf/            # PDF generation
│   ├── presentation/       # API layer
│   │   ├── api/v1/         # FastAPI routers
│   │   └── schemas/        # Pydantic schemas
│   └── main.py             # Application entry point
├── tests/                  # Test suite
├── pyproject.toml          # Project configuration
└── README.md               # This file
```

## Architecture

This project follows **Clean Architecture** principles:

- **Domain Layer**: Pure Python, no external dependencies
- **Application Layer**: Use cases, orchestrates domain logic
- **Infrastructure Layer**: External systems (DB, Excel, PDF)
- **Presentation Layer**: FastAPI REST API

Dependencies flow inward: Presentation → Application → Domain ← Infrastructure
